                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-377-18720408 t18720408-377-punishment-65"></join>Two Years' Imprisonment.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Justice Quain.</hi>
               </p>
